    "description": "Togami Electric Mfg. Co., Ltd. engages in the manufacturing and sale of industrial power distribution equipment in Japan. It offers tracing devices and measuring instruments, which include super line checkers, underground distribution fault locators, and cell line checkers; and LV control equipment comprising electromagnetic switches, including standard, economic and reversing magnetic starter/contactor, magnetic and thermal overload relay, and star-delta starter. The company also provides explosion-proof controllers, such as explosion-proof circuit breakers, combination and motor starters, and control switches; and anticorrosion controllers, including water-and corrosion-proof switches, and corrosion-proof magnetic and combination starters. In addition, it offers switchboards, which include medium-voltage power receiving and low-voltage switch boards, and motor control centers; and medium voltage products. The company distributes its products across Greece, Egypt, Saudi Arabia, Kuwait, Venezuela, the Dominican Republic, Bolivia, Thailand, Taiwan, Singapore, the Philippines, Pakistan, Malaysia, Indonesia, Hong Kong, Bangladesh, and Bahrain. Togami Electric Mfg. Co., Ltd. was founded in 1925 and is headquartered in Saga, Japan."
